  "title": "Senior/ Civil & Structural Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a leader in the construction industry that provides design and build services with an in-house multidisciplinary consultancy. Specialising in building, civil engineering, and infrastructure projects, they deliver innovative and efficient solutions to meet the evolving needs of the industry. Currently hiring for a Senior/ Civil & Structural Engineer to join the team, they will like to invite interested candidate to send your detailed resume to talent@asiasearch.com.sg.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Senior/ Civil & Structural Engineer</strong></u></p><p>Job Description:</p><ul><li>Design and oversee construction projects</li><li>Conduct site inspections to ensure compliance with safety and environmental regulations.</li><li>Collaborate with architects, contractors, and other engineers to develop project plans.</li><li>Prepare and review engineering reports, proposals, and cost estimates.</li><li>Utilize computer-aided design (CAD) software for project modeling and analysis.</li><li>Manage project timelines and budgets to ensure timely completion and cost-effectiveness.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Civil Engineering.</li><li>2 years or more experience in Building construction projects.</li><li>Good interpersonal and communication skills.</li></ul>",
